query:
SELECT e.id, e.userId, e.evaluationType, e.evaluationPeriod, e.status, COUNT(es.id) as scoreCount
FROM evaluations e
LEFT JOIN evaluationScores es ON e.id = es.evaluationId
WHERE e.userId = 1170001
GROUP BY e.id
ORDER BY e.evaluationPeriod DESC;
